2^{n+1}=2\times 2^{n}\geq 2(n+1)^2
n\geq 6,
2(n+1)^2-(n+2)^2
=2(n^2+2n+1)-(n^2+4+4n)
=2n^2+4n+2-n^2-4-4n
=n^2-2\geq0
\therefore 2(n+1)^2\geq(n+2)^2
\therefore 2^{n+1}\geq(n+2)^2
